曝光，还是过曝，过了几档，你可以根据这个数值手动调整曝光参数，也就是说调整光圈、快门和 ISO。<br><br>如果你不调整，直接拍，那确实就像你说的，任何测光模式都不会影响最终成片的效果。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"麥嘜-ᴅʀᴇᴀᴍᴇʀ","uid":"1663285","ctime":1584783672,"ip_address":"","comment_id":191360,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"14469667393","product_id":100043001,"comment_content":"刚才捣鼓了下我的佳能80d，得出一个有意思的结论：在M档即手动模式下，测光模式并不会对最终曝光产生影响。所以相机中的测光模式只是用于非手动档模式吗？在手动档下，测光模式用来做什么？","like_count":4,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1663285,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/61/35/acc2ed75.jpg","nickname":"布步次里-Mai","note":"","ucode":"B1BA13EFFC82A2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":488157,"discussion_content":"没用。\n\n但相机里一般都有个曝光指示条儿，上面会显示在当前测光模式下、在当前选择的测光点上或测光区域中，你的曝光值是多少。是欠曝，欠了几档，还是准确曝光，还是过曝，过了几档，你可以根据这个数值手动调整曝光参数，也就是说调整光圈、快门和 ISO。\n\n如果你不调整，直接拍，那确实就像你说的，任何测光模式都不会影响最终成片的效果。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1584783672,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":169715,"user_name":"mayunian","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1092049,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D38591B31F9E0C","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a9/d1/ffe56a3d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1578410659,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"65847","content":"切换成手动模式就行了啊...光圈快门 ISO 都手动自己调~","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"麥嘜-ᴅʀᴇᴀᴍᴇʀ","uid":"1663285","ctime":1578411921,"ip_address":"","comment_id":169715,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":4,"race_medal":0,"score":"10168345251","product_id":100043001,"comment_content":"当前的相机是不是都不能关闭自动测光模式？只能通过曝光补偿调整？","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1663285,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/61/35/acc2ed75.jpg","nickname":"布步次里-Mai","note":"","ucode":"B1BA13EFFC82A2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":480687,"discussion_content":"切换成手动模式就行了啊...光圈快门 ISO 都手动自己调~","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1578411921,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1092049,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a9/d1/ffe56a3d.jpg","nickname":"mayunian","note":"","ucode":"D38591B31F9E0C","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":125539,"discussion_content":"哦明白了，相机的自动测光只是为了自动调节光圈，快门和ISO。那么在手动模式下各种测光模式就没有了，对吗？那曝光补偿又是干嘛用的呢？","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1578489435,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":2,"child_discussions":[{"author":{"id":1663285,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/61/35/acc2ed75.jpg","nickname":"布步次里-Mai","note":"","ucode":"B1BA13EFFC82A2","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":1092049,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a9/d1/ffe56a3d.jpg","nickname":"mayunian","note":"","ucode":"D38591B31F9E0C","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":127003,"discussion_content":"曝光补偿是自动模式的东西。比如说，你现在让相机自动测光，它给你一套参数“F11 1/250s 200”，这是它根据它认为的中性灰得出的参数，但你现在把曝光补偿往下拉了一档，这样一来，相机给出的参数就有可能变成“F16 1/250s 200”或“F11 1/500s 200”或“F11 1/250s 100”。我经常觉得相机本身的测光偏亮，所以偶尔我用自动模式的时候，就会把曝光补偿往下拉 0.7EV，我觉得这样相机自动测光出来的效果才比较合适。",